title: The Big Suey: Nobody Cares Like Tom Brady Cares
description:
Andrew Hawkins and Ross Tucker join the show to continue our NFL talk including the trade deadline, top tier teams in the league, and to share stories from their time with Tom Brady in New England. Then, our Top 4 White Cornerbacks and Top 5 White Safeties of all-time.
